{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3646,"text":"So, this is my grandfather,"},{"time":6612,"text":"Salman Schocken,"},{"time":8113,"text":"who was born into a poor and uneducated family"},{"time":12550,"text":"with six children to feed,"},{"time":15987,"text":"and when he was 14 years old, he was forced to"},{"time":19683,"text":"drop out of school in order to help put bread on the table."},{"time":23643,"text":"He never went back to school."},{"time":27063,"text":"Instead, he went on to build a glittering empire"},{"time":31210,"text":"of department stores."},{"time":33318,"text":"Salman was the consummate perfectionist,"},{"time":36571,"text":"and every one of his stores was a jewel"},{"time":39135,"text":"of Bauhaus architecture."},{"time":41064,"text":"He was also the ultimate self-learner,"},{"time":44254,"text":"and like everything else, he did it in grand style."},{"time":47157,"text":"He surrounded himself with an entourage"},{"time":49845,"text":"of young, unknown scholars like Martin Buber"},{"time":53232,"text":"and Shai Agnon and Franz Kafka,"},{"time":56371,"text":"and he paid each one of them a monthly salary"},{"time":59296,"text":"so that they could write in peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62347,"text":"And yet, in the late '30s, Salman saw what's coming."},{"time":67284,"text":"He fled Germany, together with his family,"},{"time":70598,"text":"leaving everything else behind."},{"time":72687,"text":"His department stores confiscated,"},{"time":75897,"text":"he spent the rest of his life in a relentless pursuit"},{"time":78986,"text":"of art and culture."},{"time":81455,"text":"This high school dropout"},{"time":83394,"text":"died at the age of 82,"},{"time":85674,"text":"a formidable intellectual, cofounder and first CEO"},{"time":89803,"text":"of the Hebrew University of Jerusalem,"},{"time":91948,"text":"and founder of Schocken Books,"},{"time":93712,"text":"an acclaimed imprint that was later acquired"},{"time":97083,"text":"by Random House."},{"time":98753,"text":"Such is the power of self-study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102729,"text":"And these are my parents."},{"time":105245,"text":"They too did not enjoy the privilege of college education."},{"time":109292,"text":"They were too busy building a family and a country."},{"time":113263,"text":"And yet, just like Salman, they were lifelong,"},{"time":117291,"text":"tenacious self-learners, and our home was stacked"},{"time":121049,"text":"with thousands of books, records and artwork."},{"time":125212,"text":"I remember quite vividly my father telling me"},{"time":127608,"text":"that when everyone in the neighborhood will have a TV set,"},{"time":132440,"text":"then we'll buy a normal F.M. radio. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137058,"text":"And that's me,"},{"time":140087,"text":"I was going to say holding my first abacus,"},{"time":141811,"text":"but actually holding what my father would consider"},{"time":144822,"text":"an ample substitute to an iPad. (Laughter)"},{"time":147774,"text":"So one thing that I took from home is this notion"},{"time":151436,"text":"that educators don't necessarily have to teach."},{"time":154277,"text":"Instead, they can provide an environment and resources"},{"time":157506,"text":"that tease out your natural ability to learn on your own."},{"time":162654,"text":"Self-study, self-exploration, self-empowerment:"},{"time":166748,"text":"these are the virtues of a great education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170068,"text":"So I'd like to share with you a story about a self-study,"},{"time":174263,"text":"self-empowering computer science course"},{"time":176817,"text":"that I built, together with my brilliant colleague Noam Nisan."},{"time":181003,"text":"As you can see from the pictures, both Noam and I"},{"time":183760,"text":"had an early fascination with first principles,"},{"time":187178,"text":"and over the years, as our knowledge of"},{"time":188700,"text":"science and technology became more sophisticated,"},{"time":192275,"text":"this early awe with the basics"},{"time":195471,"text":"has only intensified."},{"time":197571,"text":"So it's not surprising that, about 12 years ago, when"},{"time":201270,"text":"Noam and I were already computer science professors,"},{"time":204752,"text":"we were equally frustrated by the same phenomenon."},{"time":208504,"text":"As computers became increasingly more complex,"},{"time":211322,"text":"our students were losing the forest for the trees,"},{"time":214526,"text":"and indeed, it is impossible to connect"},{"time":217613,"text":"with the soul of the machine if you interact"},{"time":220255,"text":"with a black box P.C. or a Mac which is shrouded"},{"time":223664,"text":"by numerous layers of closed, proprietary software."},{"time":227040,"text":"So Noam and I had this insight that if we want our students"},{"time":230730,"text":"to understand how computers work,"},{"time":232749,"text":"and understand it in the marrow of their bones,"},{"time":235837,"text":"then perhaps the best way to go about it"},{"time":237398,"text":"is to have them build a complete, working,"},{"time":241992,"text":"general-purpose, useful computer, hardware and software,"},{"time":245704,"text":"from the ground up, from first principles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249234,"text":"Now, we had to start somewhere, and so Noam and I"},{"time":253442,"text":"decided to base our cathedral, so to speak,"},{"time":256932,"text":"on the simplest possible building block,"},{"time":260071,"text":"which is something called NAND."},{"time":262872,"text":"It is nothing more than a trivial logic gate"},{"time":266810,"text":"with four input-output states."},{"time":269848,"text":"So we now start this journey by telling our students"},{"time":272514,"text":"that God gave us NAND — (Laughter) —"},{"time":274582,"text":"and told us to build a computer, and when we asked how,"},{"time":278567,"text":"God said, \"One step at a time.\""},{"time":281751,"text":"And then, following this advice, we start"},{"time":284844,"text":"with this lowly, humble NAND gate,"},{"time":287803,"text":"and we walk our students through an elaborate sequence"},{"time":289743,"text":"of projects in which they gradually build a chip set,"},{"time":293480,"text":"a hardware platform, an assembler, a virtual machine,"},{"time":297592,"text":"a basic operating system and a compiler"},{"time":301169,"text":"for a simple, Java-like language that we call \"JACK.\""},{"time":307358,"text":"The students celebrate the end of this tour de force"},{"time":309906,"text":"by using JACK to write all sorts of cool games"},{"time":312740,"text":"like Pong, Snake and Tetris."},{"time":315732,"text":"You can imagine the tremendous joy of playing"},{"time":319347,"text":"with a Tetris game that you wrote in JACK"},{"time":322371,"text":"and then compiled into machine language in a compiler"},{"time":325161,"text":"that you wrote also, and then seeing the result"},{"time":327569,"text":"running on a machine that you built starting"},{"time":330452,"text":"with nothing more than a few thousand NAND gates."},{"time":333736,"text":"It's a tremendous personal triumph of going"},{"time":336926,"text":"from first principles all the way to a fantastically complex"},{"time":341651,"text":"and useful system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344002,"text":"Noam and I worked five years to facilitate"},{"time":348399,"text":"this ascent and to create the tools and infrastructure"},{"time":351607,"text":"that will enable students to build it in one semester."},{"time":354780,"text":"And this is the great team that helped us make it happen."},{"time":358819,"text":"The trick was to decompose the computer's construction"},{"time":363066,"text":"into numerous stand-alone modules,"},{"time":366020,"text":"each of which could be individually specified,"},{"time":369920,"text":"built and unit-tested in isolation from the rest of the project."},{"time":375155,"text":"And from day one, Noam and I decided to put"},{"time":378144,"text":"all these building blocks freely available in open source"},{"time":381680,"text":"on the Web."},{"time":383160,"text":"So chip specifications, APIs, project descriptions,"},{"time":387631,"text":"software tools, hardware simulators, CPU emulators,"},{"time":391535,"text":"stacks of hundreds of slides, lectures --"},{"time":395237,"text":"we laid out everything on the Web"},{"time":397464,"text":"and invited the world to come over,"},{"time":400491,"text":"take whatever they need,"},{"time":402027,"text":"and do whatever they want with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404417,"text":"And then something fascinating happened."},{"time":408316,"text":"The world came."},{"time":409899,"text":"And in short order, thousands of people"},{"time":413057,"text":"were building our machine."},{"time":414601,"text":"And NAND2Tetris became one of the first"},{"time":418525,"text":"massive, open, online courses,"},{"time":421755,"text":"although seven years ago we had no idea that what"},{"time":424499,"text":"we were doing is called MOOCs."},{"time":426660,"text":"We just observed how self-organized courses"},{"time":430518,"text":"were kind of spontaneously spawning"},{"time":433600,"text":"out of our materials."},{"time":434983,"text":"For example, Pramode C.E.,"},{"time":438074,"text":"an engineer from Kerala, India,"},{"time":439983,"text":"has organized groups of self-learners"},{"time":441792,"text":"who build our computer under his good guidance."},{"time":444836,"text":"And Parag Shah, another engineer, from Mumbai,"},{"time":447858,"text":"has unbundled our projects into smaller,"},{"time":450703,"text":"more manageable bites that he now serves"},{"time":452725,"text":"in his pioneering do-it-yourself computer science program."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456527,"text":"The people who are attracted to these courses"},{"time":459938,"text":"typically have a hacker mentality."},{"time":462358,"text":"They want to figure out how things work,"},{"time":464463,"text":"and they want to do it in groups,"},{"time":466223,"text":"like this hackers club in Washington, D.C.,"},{"time":469034,"text":"that uses our materials to offer community courses."},{"time":472699,"text":"And because these materials are widely available"},{"time":475645,"text":"and open-source, different people take them"},{"time":478339,"text":"to very different and unpredictable directions."},{"time":481282,"text":"For example, Yu Fangmin, from Guangzhou,"},{"time":484195,"text":"has used FPGA technology"},{"time":487041,"text":"to build our computer and show others how to do the same"},{"time":490766,"text":"using a video clip, and Ben Craddock developed"},{"time":494129,"text":"a very nice computer game that unfolds"},{"time":497730,"text":"inside our CPU architecture, which is quite a complex"},{"time":502699,"text":"3D maze that Ben developed"},{"time":505184,"text":"using the Minecraft 3D simulator engine."},{"time":509092,"text":"The Minecraft community went bananas over this project,"},{"time":512110,"text":"and Ben became an instant media celebrity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":515494,"text":"And indeed, for quite a few people,"},{"time":518396,"text":"taking this NAND2Tetris pilgrimage, if you will,"},{"time":522473,"text":"has turned into a life-changing experience."},{"time":525185,"text":"For example, take Dan Rounds, who is a music"},{"time":528374,"text":"and math major from East Lansing, Michigan."},{"time":531143,"text":"A few weeks ago, Dan posted a victorious post"},{"time":534587,"text":"on our website, and I'd like to read it to you."},{"time":537207,"text":"So here's what Dan said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540665,"text":"\"I did the coursework because understanding computers"},{"time":543477,"text":"is important to me, just like literacy and numeracy,"},{"time":546823,"text":"and I made it through. I never worked harder on anything,"},{"time":549840,"text":"never been challenged to this degree."},{"time":552549,"text":"But given what I now feel capable of doing,"},{"time":554936,"text":"I would certainly do it again."},{"time":557094,"text":"To anyone considering NAND2Tetris,"},{"time":559344,"text":"it's a tough journey, but you'll be profoundly changed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":563090,"text":"So Dan demonstrates the many self-learners"},{"time":567990,"text":"who take this course off the Web, on their own traction,"},{"time":572636,"text":"on their own initiative, and it's quite amazing because"},{"time":577225,"text":"these people cannot care less about"},{"time":581812,"text":"grades."},{"time":583054,"text":"They are doing it because of one motivation only."},{"time":586959,"text":"They have a tremendous passion to learn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590445,"text":"And with that in mind,"},{"time":592369,"text":"I'd like to say a few words about traditional college grading."},{"time":596973,"text":"I'm sick of it."},{"time":599333,"text":"We are obsessed with grades"},{"time":600766,"text":"because we are obsessed with data,"},{"time":602632,"text":"and yet grading takes away all the fun from failing,"},{"time":607219,"text":"and a huge part of education"},{"time":609695,"text":"is about failing."},{"time":611286,"text":"Courage, according to Churchill,"},{"time":613761,"text":"is the ability to go from one defeat to another"},{"time":616707,"text":"without losing enthusiasm. (Laughter)"},{"time":619321,"text":"And [Joyce] said that mistakes"},{"time":623151,"text":"are the portals of discovery."},{"time":624620,"text":"And yet we don't tolerate mistakes,"},{"time":627966,"text":"and we worship grades."},{"time":629275,"text":"So we collect your B pluses and your A minuses"},{"time":633063,"text":"and we aggregate them into a number like 3.4,"},{"time":635900,"text":"which is stamped on your forehead"},{"time":637811,"text":"and sums up who you are."},{"time":640254,"text":"Well, in my opinion, we went too far with this nonsense,"},{"time":643537,"text":"and grading became degrading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646218,"text":"So with that, I'd like to say a few words about upgrading,"},{"time":651119,"text":"and share with you a glimpse from my current project,"},{"time":655544,"text":"which is different from the previous one,"},{"time":657574,"text":"but it shares exactly the same characteristics"},{"time":659588,"text":"of self-learning, learning by doing,"},{"time":663415,"text":"self-exploration and community-building,"},{"time":666190,"text":"and this project deals with K-12 math education,"},{"time":672050,"text":"beginning with early age math,"},{"time":673954,"text":"and we do it on tablets because we believe that"},{"time":678447,"text":"math, like anything else, should be taught hands on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682852,"text":"So here's what we do. Basically, we developed"},{"time":686007,"text":"numerous mobile apps, every one of them explaining"},{"time":689765,"text":"a particular concept in math."},{"time":691262,"text":"So for example, let's take area."},{"time":694703,"text":"When you deal with a concept like area --"},{"time":697175,"text":"well, we also provide a set of tools that the child"},{"time":702419,"text":"is invited to experiment with in order to learn."},{"time":705050,"text":"So if area is what interests us, then one thing"},{"time":709003,"text":"which is natural to do is to tile the area"},{"time":713141,"text":"of this particular shape and simply count"},{"time":716791,"text":"how many tiles it takes to cover it completely."},{"time":720654,"text":"And this little exercise here gives you a first"},{"time":723136,"text":"good insight of the notion of area."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726565,"text":"Moving along, what about the area of this figure?"},{"time":729355,"text":"Well, if you try to tile it, it doesn't work too well, does it."},{"time":734012,"text":"So instead, you can experiment"},{"time":736316,"text":"with these different tools here by some process"},{"time":738996,"text":"of guided trial and error,"},{"time":741035,"text":"and at some point you will discover that one thing"},{"time":743873,"text":"that you can do among several legitimate transformations"},{"time":746961,"text":"is the following one. You can cut the figure,"},{"time":749792,"text":"you can rearrange the parts, you can glue them"},{"time":753408,"text":"and then proceed to tile just like we did before."},{"time":756525,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":761800,"text":"Now this particular transformation"},{"time":764523,"text":"did not change the area of the original figure,"},{"time":768507,"text":"so a six-year-old who plays with this"},{"time":770694,"text":"has just discovered a clever algorithm"},{"time":773578,"text":"to compute the area of any given parallelogram."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777618,"text":"We don't replace teachers, by the way."},{"time":779474,"text":"We believe that teachers should be empowered, not replaced."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782603,"text":"Moving along, what about the area of a triangle?"},{"time":785898,"text":"So after some guided trial and error,"},{"time":788693,"text":"the child will discover, with or without help,"},{"time":792628,"text":"that he or she can duplicate the original figure"},{"time":796486,"text":"and then take the result, transpose it,"},{"time":799894,"text":"glue it to the original and then proceed [with] what we did before:"},{"time":803642,"text":"cut, rearrange, paste — oops— paste and glue,"},{"time":811370,"text":"and tile."},{"time":812966,"text":"Now this transformation has doubled the area"},{"time":816793,"text":"of the original figure, and therefore we have just learned"},{"time":820643,"text":"that the area of the triangle equals the area of this rectangle"},{"time":824409,"text":"divided by two."},{"time":826863,"text":"But we discovered it by self-exploration."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830311,"text":"So, in addition to learning some useful geometry,"},{"time":836391,"text":"the child has been exposed to some pretty sophisticated"},{"time":840778,"text":"science strategies, like reduction,"},{"time":843805,"text":"which is the art of"},{"time":846719,"text":"transforming a complex problem into a simple one,"},{"time":850305,"text":"or generalization, which is at the heart"},{"time":852674,"text":"of any scientific discipline,"},{"time":855517,"text":"or the fact that some properties are invariant"},{"time":858107,"text":"under some transformations."},{"time":861131,"text":"And all this is something that a very young child"},{"time":864416,"text":"can pick up using such mobile apps."},{"time":868725,"text":"So presently, we are doing the following:"},{"time":871819,"text":"First of all, we are decomposing the K-12 math curriculum"},{"time":876128,"text":"into numerous such apps."},{"time":879019,"text":"And because we cannot do it on our own,"},{"time":881596,"text":"we've developed a very fancy authoring tool"},{"time":884690,"text":"that any author, any parent or actually anyone"},{"time":887965,"text":"who has an interest in math education,"},{"time":890318,"text":"can use this authoring tool to develop similar apps"},{"time":893590,"text":"on tablets without programming."},{"time":896995,"text":"And finally, we are putting together an adaptive ecosystem"},{"time":900215,"text":"that will match different learners"},{"time":903043,"text":"with different apps according to their evolving learning style."}]},{"cues":[{"time":908420,"text":"The driving force behind this project"},{"time":910941,"text":"is my colleague Shmulik London,"},{"time":913888,"text":"and, you see, just like"},{"time":916532,"text":"Salman did about 90 years ago,"},{"time":920605,"text":"the trick is to surround yourself with brilliant people,"},{"time":924576,"text":"because at the end,"},{"time":927332,"text":"it's all about people."},{"time":929235,"text":"And a few years ago, I was walking in Tel Aviv"},{"time":932654,"text":"and I saw this graffiti on a wall,"},{"time":935484,"text":"and I found it so compelling"},{"time":937275,"text":"that by now I preach it to my students,"},{"time":939418,"text":"and I'd like to try to preach it to you."},{"time":941684,"text":"Now, I don't know how many people here are familiar"},{"time":943424,"text":"with the term \"mensch.\""},{"time":945252,"text":"It basically means to be human"},{"time":947860,"text":"and to do the right thing."},{"time":949795,"text":"And with that, what this graffiti says is,"},{"time":952224,"text":"\"High-tech schmigh-tech."},{"time":954310,"text":"The most important thing is to be a mensch.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":956873,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":960268,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}